SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Description], [p].[Category], [p].[Brand], [p].[Specifications], [p].[Warranty], CASE
    WHEN [p].[Image] IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [p].[Image], [p].[Quantity]
FROM [Carts] AS [c]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [c].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
WHERE [c].[UserId] = @__userId_0

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [o].[Id], [o].[OrderDate], [o].[ProductId], [o].[UserName]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[AdminId] = @__adminId_0
    ORDER BY [o].[OrderDate] DESC
) AS [o0]
INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
ORDER BY [o0].[OrderDate] DESC
